com.indeed.vw.wrapper.api.parameters

Interface SGDVowpalWabbitBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DebuggingOptions, FeatureEngineeringFunctions, FeatureSelectionOptions, LinkAndLossOptions, MiscOptions, OptionsToSaveAndLoadModel, OptionToExchangeRAMForQuality, PredictionBoundaryOptions, RegularizationOptions, UpdatesOptions
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    VowpalWabbit.Builder

    public interface SGDVowpalWabbitBuilder
extends UpdatesOptions, RegularizationOptions, PredictionBoundaryOptions, LinkAndLossOptions, FeatureEngineeringFunctions, OptionsToSaveAndLoadModel, DebuggingOptions, FeatureSelectionOptions, OptionToExchangeRAMForQuality, MiscOptions
    This interface specify small subset of available options with some additional documentation.

    In 90% [1] of cases you will need only these options.

    Though I highly recommend to follow https://github.com/JohnLangford/vowpal_wabbit/wiki/Command-line-arguments and read some tutorials.
